run checkin_files script then
it will stop and show a message 
"start app_writer first then start app_reader in separate window"
"hit return to remove module"

open a new tab or window and start reader app
sudo ./app_reader /dev/scartch_node
as the scull is empty read_dev will stop on wait_for_completion() when write_dev executes completion()
read_dev starts reading.

open a new tab or window and start writer app
sudo ./app_writer /dev/scartch_node

